metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Super Mario Odyssey Trailer is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
Super Mario Odyssey Trailer is written in the key of C Major.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the most common key in all of popular music. 

See the C Major Cheat Sheet for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: I believe the F#o in the chorus to be borrowed from lydian (#ivo) and not a secondary chord because it is not directly proceeded by a G (V) chord
